o\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"his new-found fame\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Henrik Christiansen, better known as 'muffin man', is still flabbergasted by the degree to which his social media following has exploded over the course of these Games, ever since he started documenting his love for the \\\"11 out of 10\\u2033 sweet treats inParis.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"muffin man\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"the degree\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"his social media\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"his love\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"10\\u2033 sweet treats\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"inParis\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four of hisTikTokshave attracted more than 10 million views - the most popular video nearing nearly twice that at 17.8 million.\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hisTikTokshave\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 10 million views\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the most popular video\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly twice that\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansen, 27, told the PA news agency: \\\"I think three weeks ago I had 3000 followers on TikTok, now I am at almost half a million.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7095273958466785e-45, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Christiansen\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"3000 followers\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's been unreal.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You never really think it's going to happen.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You see other people blowing up like that and then you think it's never going to happen to you, but here I am.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think as professional athletes we are definitely in the entertainment industry, so we kind of need to produce content by doing the sport and also being on social media.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"professional athletes\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"the entertainment industry\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to produce content that other people want to watch.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's how we can make money, so if I am now able to earn more money from doing my sport and being able to continue doing that for longer, I would love that.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"more money\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I still have to see yet.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently I have not dived too much into it, but hopefully I can make a little bit by doing it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one video, Christiansen is seen strutting down the street, two muffins in each hand, to the tune of the bass-heavy Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas theme song.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one video\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"Christiansen\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"each hand\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"the tune\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"the bass-heavy Grand Theft Auto\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"San Andreas theme song\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In another, he is \\\"caught\\\" chocolate-handed with a stash in his bedside drawer.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"a stash\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"his bedside drawer\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are also glimpses of competition life, including one poking fun at ongoing concerns over conditions in the Seine ahead of Christiansen's open-water 10 kilometres event.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999998787575424, \"rank\": 1.2124096912206662e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"glimpses\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"competition life\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"one poking fun\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"ongoing concerns\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"conditions\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"Christiansen's open-water 10 kilometres event\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think three weeks ago I had 3000 followers on TikTok, now I am at almost half a million.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7095273958466785e-45, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3000 followers\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's been unreal It was captioned: \\\"Guys if I do not survive this, tell my fans I love them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Guys\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"my fans\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris was a third Olympics for Christiansen, who also took part in the men's 1500 metres freestyle and the men's 800 metres freestyle.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2346, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.474616822942173e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a third Olympics\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"Christiansen\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 1500 metres freestyle\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 800 metres freestyle\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew in advance he wanted to document his experience on TikTok, and just happened to pick up one of the gooey-centered muffins during his first meal in the village.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7095273958466785e-45, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"his experience\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the gooey-centered muffins\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"his first meal\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The savvyScandinavianis a shining example of the special genre of stories that feel like they can only come out of an Olympic or Paralympic Games, elevating the profile of a hard-working and dedicated athlete who would not usually attract anywhere near the same level of attention.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The savvyScandinavianis\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"a shining example\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"the special genre\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic or Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"the profile\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"a hard-working and dedicated athlete\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"the same level\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week, he posed for a picture with the visiting Crown Prince Haakon, heir apparent to the Norwegian throne.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3036, \"end\": 3045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\", \"score\": 0.9393161491320046, \"rank\": 0.054618463154217096, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norwegian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a picture\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"the visiting Crown Prince Haakon\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"heir\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I never in my life thought that I would be taking fan photos in the Olympic village, because that's (usually) only the biggest athletes, but I have been doing it.Peoplehave been coming up to me, chatting about the muffin, having a chat.\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"fan photos\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"only the biggest athletes\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"Peoplehave\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3237}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffin\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"a chat\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been really fun.\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not really describe it.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also log off of all other social media during championships, and that's what I have been doing for the past nine or 10 years.\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all other social media\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3396}, {\"ngram\": \"championships\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"the past nine or 10 years\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I try not to spend too much time focusing on that while I am still competing, but now that I am finished I guess I can indulge a bit more and see everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much time\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3521}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I never in my life thought that I would be taking fan photos in the Olympic village, because that's (usually) only the biggest athletes Tony Dore became the official chief baker of the Olympic village after topping a podium of his own when he won a baguette-making competition held by Sodexo Live, who provide the village catering.\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3791, \"end\": 3795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\", \"score\": 0.9999997116947685, \"rank\": 2.486780876746982e-07, \"text\": \"Dore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\"}, {\"begin\": 3935, \"end\": 3941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3667}, {\"ngram\": \"fan photos\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"only the biggest athletes\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3784}, {\"ngram\": \"the official chief baker\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3849}, {\"ngram\": \"a podium\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3872}, {\"ngram\": \"a baguette-making competition\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3925}, {\"ngram\": \"the village catering\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 3979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the muffins are more standard-fare for Sodexco, Dore was responsible for coming up with another baked treat that was both easily portable for athletes and responsive to their nutritional needs.\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 4182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4037, \"end\": 4041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\", \"score\": 0.9999997116947685, \"rank\": 2.486780876746982e-07, \"text\": \"Dore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"more standard-fare\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4023}, {\"ngram\": \"Sodexco\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4035}, {\"ngram\": \"another baked treat\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4139}, {\"ngram\": \"their nutritional needs\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enter the pain au cacao, a twist on the classic French pain au chocolat, but using almost no butter or sugar and weighing in at under 130 calories per portion.\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4202, \"end\": 4207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chocolate\", \"score\": 0.997397765129216, \"rank\": 0.0026090241323729205, \"text\": \"cacao\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chocolate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chocolate\"}, {\"begin\": 4232, \"end\": 4238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9964634673328456, \"rank\": 0.0034902760518452885, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4198}, {\"ngram\": \"a twist\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"au chocolat\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"almost no butter\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4283}, {\"ngram\": \"sugar\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"under 130 calories\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4330}, {\"ngram\": \"portion\", \"from\": 4335, \"to\": 4342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Saturday, had the chance to meet the man who made his muffins viral, saying: \\\"Maybe we can ask him to try my cocoa bread to see how he's feeling and if the taste is good.\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 4348, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 4362, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4388}, {\"ngram\": \"his muffins\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4409}, {\"ngram\": \"my cocoa bread\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"the taste\", \"from\": 4500, \"to\": 4509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have the answer, because all the athletes love them.\\\"\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the answer\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4542}, {\"ngram\": \"all the athletes\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dore has woken up at four o'clock every day of the Olympics to prepare his products, which include 600 French baguettes and 900 cocoa breads per day.\", \"from\": 4582, \"to\": 4731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4582, \"end\": 4586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\", \"score\": 0.9999997116947685, \"rank\": 2.486780876746982e-07, \"text\": \"Dore\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gweedore\